title: ScannerEventResponseInfo
name: ScannerEventResponseInfo
description: A ScannerEventResponseInfo is passed to the responseScannerEvent delegate during scanner mode when a scan is detected. It contains all necessary information needed about the relevant operation. ScannerEventResponseInfo inherits from ResponseInfo so it includes the status string and xml dictionary in addition to scanCode string.

properties.name: statusCode
properties.description: A numerical representation of the status.

properties.name: xml
properties.description: Feedback with xml details about transaction from the card reader.
